title: Export Code Blocks to File From Org Mode Using Tangle
tags: @zettel _method orgmode
roam-id: 28fc4efd-3639-43bf-a220-e722daf7868c
type: text/markdown

+begin~src~ bash :tangle /path/to/file.sh #!/usr/bin/env bash echo \"hello world\" +end~src~

when you run this code block your code will be exported to `/path/to/file.sh`
